snippet.textDisplay:
No disrespect to Anuv Jain but it's honestly disheartening to see that despite having sung such a core part of the song, Sarthak Kalyani (who sang the sargam) doesn’t even get a single screen presence. He’s worked so hard over the years and his contribution has truly taken this track to another level, yet goes unnoticed.
That said, feels good Sarthak is finally getting a platform like this, and I genuinely wish him all the success he deserves in the times to come. This is just the beginning of bigger things ahead for him. 🙌🏼
